### Admin - stats
GET {{host}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Listings - create
POST {{host}}/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "2BR Apartment for Rent",
  "description": "Nice 2 bedroom apartment near the market.",
  "listingType": "RENT",
  "price": 200,
  "currency": "USD",
  "location": "Kabul",
  "address": "Street 1, Near Market",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "contactVisibility": "SHOW_SELLER",
  "metadata": { "floor": 3, "furnished": true, "parking": "shared" },
  "expiresAt": "2025-10-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "images": [
    { "url": "/uploads/listings/1/img1.jpg", "alt": "kitchen view", "position": 0 },
    { "url": "/uploads/listings/1/img2.jpg", "alt": "living room", "position": 1 }
  ]
}

### Listings - get
GET {{host}}/listings/cmff5cbxv0041tu5c1vf24px8

### Listings - list approved
GET {{host}}/listings

### Listings - list pending (admin)
GET {{host}}/listings/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Listings - approve (admin)
POST {{host}}/listings/{{listingId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactVisibility": "SHOW_SELLER",
  "notes": "Approved by admin",
  "approvedAt": "2025-09-10T12:00:00.000Z",
  "approvedById": "user0@example.com",
  "meta": { "moderator": "admin@example.com", "reason": "meets guidelines" }
}

