### Themes - list all themes (admin only)
GET {{host}}/themes
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Themes - get default theme (admin only)
GET {{host}}/themes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Themes - create (admin)
POST {{host}}/themes
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "default",
  "tokens": {
    "light": { "color": { "primary": "#0d6efd" } },
    "dark": { "color": { "primary": "#66b2ff" } }
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### Themes - update (admin)
PUT {{host}}/themes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tokens": {
    "light": { "color": { "primary": "#0d6efd", "background": "#ffffff" }, "spacing": { "md": 16 } },
    "dark": { "color": { "primary": "#66b2ff", "background": "#0b1220" }, "spacing": { "md": 16 } }
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### Listings - update by id
PUT {{host}}/listings/{{listingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "price": 250,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Listings - patch by id
PATCH {{host}}/listings/{{listingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

